{
  "number": 91,
  "name": "سُورَةُ الشَّمۡسِ",
  "englishName": "Ash-Shams",
  "ayahs": [
    {
      "number": 1,
      "text": "By the sun and its brightness",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 2,
      "text": "And [by] the moon when it follows it",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 3,
      "text": "And [by] the day when it displays it",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 4,
      "text": "And [by] the night when it covers it",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 5,
      "text": "And [by] the sky and He who constructed it",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 6,
      "text": "And [by] the earth and He who spread it",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 7,
      "text": "And [by] the soul and He who proportioned it",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 8,
      "text": "And inspired it [with discernment of] its wickedness and its righteousness,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 9,
      "text": "He has succeeded who purifies it,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 10,
      "text": "And he has failed who instills it [with corruption].",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 11,
      "text": "Thamud denied [their prophet] by reason of their transgression,",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 12,
      "text": "When the most wretched of them was sent forth.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 13,
      "text": "And the messenger of Allah [Salih] said to them, \"[Do not harm] the she-camel of Allah or [prevent her from] her drink.\"",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 14,
      "text": "But they denied him and hamstrung her. So their Lord brought down upon them destruction for their sin and made it equal [upon all of them].",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    },
    {
      "number": 15,
      "text": "And He does not fear the consequence thereof.",
      "juz": 30,
      "manzil": 7,
      "page": 595,
      "ruku": 533,
      "hizbQuarter": 238,
      "sajda": false
    }
  ]
}